<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Coin Toss Game</title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fasthand&family=Josefin+Sans&family=Trispace&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="favicon.ico">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="font-awesome.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">

  
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Coin Toss Game</h1>
  <h2>Feeling Lucky?</h2>


  <h3>"They say humans are irrational creatures... gambling doesn't get them anything, they only lose something. But even so, we still gamble. We do that because we enjoy the risk."</h3>
  <ul class="messages">
  <% for(var i=0; i<messages.length; i++) {%>
    <li class="message">
      <span><%= messages[i].personChoice %></span>
      <span><%= messages[i].flipResult %></span>
      <span><%= messages[i].theFinalAnswer %></span>
   
      <span><i class="fa fa-trash" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </li>
  <% } %>
  </ul>

  <h2>Heads or Tails?</h2>

  <form action="/messages" method="POST">
    <input type="text" placeholder="enter your choice"name="personChoice">
    
    <button type="submit">Submit</button>
  </form>

  <script src="main.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
